      "text": "p_ỹ(n) = P_q(n)  for all n ∈ ℤ",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:39:05.989Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:39:05.989Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "equation_meaning",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 165,
      "y": 470,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "text": "→ optimizing differential entropy of ỹ  ≈  optimizing discrete entropy of q",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:39:05.989Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:39:05.989Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "convolution_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 750,
